    <li class="explanation">Make test work for us, not against us</li>
    <li>Continuous delivery with speed and quality</li>
    <li class="explanation">Move fast and reliably, no breaking many things</li>
    <li>Distributed consistency and resilience</li>
    <li>Universalist. With deep focus</li>
    <li>Loves legacy</li>
    <li class="explanation">One just has to know how to cook this matured dish</li>
